Overview:
This project focuses on building a modern, responsive front-end for the Threads & Co. clothing store.
Objectives:
Improve user experience and navigation
Add mobile-first design
Integrate product filtering, search, and reviews
Match brand style with updated design system
Tech Stack:
React 18 with Vite
Tailwind CSS for styling
React Router for navigation
Axios for API requests
Key Pages:
Home
Product Listing (Men, Women, Accessories)
Product Detail
Shopping Cart
Checkout
About Us
Contact

Features:
Grid layout of products (4 per row, responsive)
Filtering by Category, Size, Color, and Price
Search bar with debounce
Sort dropdown (Price: Low to High, High to Low, Popularity)
Pagination (12 items per page)
Components Used:
`<ProductCard />`
`<FilterSidebar />`
`<SearchBar />`
`<Pagination />`
User Flow:
User lands on `/products`
Filters and search update URL query params
Products fetched from `/api/products` with filters

Steps:
Shipping Information
Payment Method
Order Review
Confirmation
Validation:
Real-time form validation
Stripe payment integration (test keys for dev)
Security:
All requests go through HTTPS
Stripe handles PCI compliance
Success Page:
Order summary
"Continue Shopping" CTA
Dinner idea: chicken and rice
